$$ Integrate both sides : $$
\begin{align}
\int\frac{y+1}{y-1}dy & =\int\frac{x+2}{x-3}dx\\
\int 1+\frac{2}{y-1}dy &=\int 1+\frac{5}{x-3}dx\\
y+2\ln|y-1|&=x+5\ln|x-3|+C\\
